            <thetext>The iterateCachedRows() method of the remote table model does not give the possibility to break out of the loop once the user-provided iterator function decides it does not need to continue.

This would be a nice optimization especially since the remote model only allows stepping through the cached rows by using the above method.

A solution would be that returning null from the iterator function breaks from the loop.</thetext>
